        dc:description           "FIGURE 18. Ilyocypris tibeta n. sp., male and female. (A) Male RV, exterior view (WOC37); (B) female LV, exterior view (WOC45); (C) male LV, interior view (WOC37); (D) female RV, interior view (WOC45); (E) male RV, dorsal view (WOC35); (F) male LV, dorsal view (WOC35); (G) male LV, interior view (WOC39); (H) enlargement of postero-ventral part of male LV (WOC37), showing marginal ripplets; (I) enlargement of antero-ventral part of male LV (WOC37), showing marginal ripplets. Scale bar: A–G = 200 μm; H = 110 μm; I = 105 μm." ;
